The literature was searched using PubMed and google scholar search engines. Papers from between 1966 and 2017 were included. The search was made using keywords such as 
 N. sativa and phytochemistry; 
 N. sativa and pharmacological properties; 
 N. sativa and immunomodulatory; 
 N. sativa and antihistaminic; 
 N. sativa and hepatoprotective; 
 N. sativa and obesity; 
 N. sativa and cardiovascular disease etc. An attempt was made to document relevant literature that is only focused on 
 N. sativa. The review includes a total of 8 clinical trials.
